WEBVTT

00:00.828 --> 00:02.748
Previously on Crazy Ex-Girlfriend...

00:02.773 --> 00:06.014
I need to confront my
ex-fiancé, who jilted me

00:06.039 --> 00:08.898
at the altar seconds before
our wedding two weeks ago.

00:08.930 --> 00:10.560
I want everyone to hear

00:10.585 --> 00:12.898
all of the terrible things he did to me

00:12.923 --> 00:15.210
and all the terrible
things he made me do.

00:15.227 --> 00:17.068
She admitted she moved
here just to stalk me.

00:17.093 --> 00:19.229
I'm telling you, Rebecca's crazy.

00:19.231 --> 00:21.832
The only person who sounds
crazy right now is you.

00:21.834 --> 00:24.420
Hey, Paula. It's me, Father Brah.
We have an emergency.

00:24.445 --> 00:26.236
- It's about Rebecca.
- _

00:26.238 --> 00:27.938
Instead of prison, she was sentenced

00:27.940 --> 00:29.389
to a psychiatric hospital.

00:29.414 --> 00:30.507
Oh, my God.

00:30.509 --> 00:32.042
It's like we never really knew her.

00:32.043 --> 00:33.143
Yeah, you're screwed.

00:33.145 --> 00:34.211
I feel things for you.

00:34.213 --> 00:35.712
I got to get the hell out of town.

00:35.714 --> 00:37.714
I'll take you wherever you want to go.

00:37.716 --> 00:38.815
Thank you for saving me.

00:39.164 --> 00:40.317
Rebecca, wait.

00:40.319 --> 00:41.885
Paula called. You cannot leave.

00:41.887 --> 00:43.420
Uh, just, uh, run! Just go around her.

00:43.422 --> 00:44.921
- It's fine. Just go around her.
- What? Okay.

00:44.923 --> 00:46.423
- Giddy-up! Giddy-up, horsey!
- No, I'm serious. Stop.

00:46.425 --> 00:48.258
- All right, she's in my way now.
- You cannot go.

00:48.260 --> 00:51.027
Rebecca, wait. We need
to talk about this.

00:55.067 --> 00:56.900
We know everything that happened.

00:56.902 --> 01:00.170
About Robert, your arrest,
your stay in the hospital.

01:00.172 --> 01:01.271
Hos... ♪ La, la, la ♪

01:01.273 --> 01:02.606
