01:02.608 --> 01:04.840
Just... Nathaniel, it's
fine. Just ignore them.

01:04.843 --> 01:06.076
Just-just-just barrel on through.

01:06.078 --> 01:07.859
- Let's go to Roma. Come on.
- Look.

01:07.884 --> 01:09.813
Obviously, there's something
going on between you two.

01:09.815 --> 01:12.616
I mean, you're doing an Officer
and a Gentleman type of thing.

01:12.618 --> 01:13.850
