- Okay, it's fine.

01:13.852 --> 01:16.486
Nathaniel, buddy, trust me.

01:16.488 --> 01:18.989
This is a lot more
complicated than it seems.

01:18.991 --> 01:20.991
Okay, Rebecca, I don't
know what's going on.

01:21.016 --> 01:23.460
No. Okay. It's...
What-what happened is they're...

01:23.462 --> 01:24.961
they're-they're being histrionic

01:24.963 --> 01:26.897
because they found out
something about my past,

01:26.899 --> 01:28.298
