without my consent.

02:50.482 --> 02:51.548
Nathaniel, pick me back up.

02:51.550 --> 02:52.582
Pick me back up. Come on.

02:52.584 --> 02:54.150
- Rebecca, hang on.
- Pick me back up.

02:54.175 --> 02:56.809
Rebecca, I don't really know
what's going on right now.

02:58.924 --> 03:01.091
Wow.

03:01.093 --> 03:02.459
You, too, Nathaniel?

03:02.461 --> 03:04.894
Huh. No, I get it.

03:04.896 --> 03:06.429
You've been, you've
been texting with them

03:06.431 --> 03:07.864
